10.body: <input> = Non Required. {input} = Required. /help - Gives the support server invite link and url to this documenation. /mine - Opens the HellForge Mining Menu. /inventory - View your inventory. /craft - Opens the crafting menu. ^ This command requires the Level 10+ Milestone to be completed.
10.title: Primary Commands

11.body: <input> = Non Required. {input} = Required. /balance - View your networth breakdown. /deposit {amount} - Deposit the inputted amount into your Bank. /withdraw {amount} - Withdraw the inputted amount from your Bank. /shop - View the shop and its items. /buy {item} {amount} - Buy items from the shop.
11.title: Economy Commands

15.body: Basic Breakdown: P = Power (resource gain) G = Grade (allows you to mine rarer resources.) D = Durability (if it hits 0 you cant use your pickaxe unless you use /repair-pickaxes
